attributes.title: WORST APP EVER!
attributes.review: I never, and I mean never have written a review for an app because I didn’t think it was worth my time. However this app goes above and beyond at being TERRIBLE! The app gives off the WORST vibes I have ever felt. DO NOT USE THIS APP OR DOWNLOAD IT! ITS A WASTE OF TIME! I WISH THERE WAS A LOWER RATING SO I COULD GIVE IT A -1000000000000 stars but sadly there is not. SUPER GLITCHY AND LAGGY! Lots of pop up ads, etc. Can’t even go a minute on this app without 10 ads popping up in your face. I’m disappointed to say the least... not sure what I expect but this was not it.
